## Tool Tips

- `archiver_read`: Parse natural language time references —
  "last hour", "yesterday", "since Monday" — into start_time/end_time.
- `execute`: Lives on the `python` server. Default to `execution_mode: "readonly"`;
  use `"write"` only when the code needs to write to the control system.
{% set ariel_enabled = servers | selectattr("name", "equalto", "ariel") | selectattr("enabled") | list | length > 0 %}
